事件循环：\n  ```dart\n  onError: (data) {\n    add(ImSocketErrorReceived(data[\
'message\'] as String? ?? \'Socket error\'));\n  },\n  ```\n并在 `ImBloc` 中注册
`on<ImSocketErrorReceived>((event, emit) => emit(ImError(event.message)));`\n- *
